<p>Borrowing the words of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rjb-r" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610156090" alt="RJB_R" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rjb-r" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;">RJB_R</a></span>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p><em>This is a just-for-fun type of page for people to list their accomplishments and provide badges for display on their author pages.</em></p>
</blockquote>
<p>The primary goal of this page is a visually neat way to showcase user's achievements, as well as to encourage community engagement. All the badges below aim to be as vote-independent as possible.</p>
<p>Since I can not enforce the requirements for these, this will based on an honor system, in which I hope everyone strives to give their best shot, and remembers to have fun!</p>
<hr />
