<div style="text-align: center;">
<h3 id="toc0"><span>Achievements Unlocked</span></h3>
<h5 id="toc1"><span>(out of <span style="color: #cea0ff">16</span>)</span></h5>
</div>
<p><a href="/estrellayoshte">EstrellaYoshte</a> - 2<br />
<a href="/ihp-s-author-page">Ihp</a> - 5<br />
<a href="/jakdragonx-rage-collection">JakdragonX</a> - 3<br />
<a href="/this-page-intentionally-left-blank">HarryBlank</a> - 3<br />
<a href="/yossipossi-authorphage">Yossipossi</a> - 5<br />
<a href="/researcher-nyka-s-file">Nykacolaquantum</a> - 2<br />
<a href="http://scp-wiki-de.wikidot.com/dr-rabes-personalakte">Einer von Rabe</a> - 6</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="casercontainer">
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc2"><span>TSF</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/tsf.png" width="160px" alt="tsf.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc3"><span>Ten Steps Forward</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Have 10 pages published on the wiki.<br />
(Fragment pages do not count, if you're wondering.)</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc4"><span>MWW</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/mww.png" width="160px" alt="mww.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc5"><span>Dr. Worldwide</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>A work of yours is translated to 5 or more foreign languages, OR you have translated 6 works from one language to another.</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc6"><span>CCC</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/ccc.png" width="160px" alt="ccc.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc7"><span>Canon Crossover Central</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Write an article involving 3 (or more) canons. Tales series and other incorporated settings with dedicated hubs are permitted for the purpose of this achievement.</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc8"><span>SEK</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/sek.png" width="160px" alt="sek.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc9"><span>The SEXTANK Initiative</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>You have written: <strong>S</strong>afe, <strong>E</strong>uclid, <strong>K</strong>eter, <strong>T</strong>haumiel, <strong>N</strong>eutralized, E<strong>x</strong>plained + <strong>A</strong>nother Esoteric-class.<br />
(The absence of Object Class altogether does not qualify as esoteric.)</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc10"><span>SCL</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/scl.png" width="160px" alt="scl.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc11"><span>Social Butterfly</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Leave detailed and constructive critique in the comments 20 times.<br />
Use your judgement as to what qualifies as detailed and constructive. Ideas and draft critiques also count.</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc12"><span>CLB</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/clb.png" width="160px" alt="clb.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc13"><span>Thank You for Your Cooperation</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Collaborate with at least 7 other authors.<br />
This could be 7 different co-authored pages or one co-authored page with your 7 co-authors, and everything in-between (You must be credited as a co-author to qualify.)</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc14"><span>DDA</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/dda.png" width="160px" alt="dda.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc15"><span>Double Double Agent</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Write 4 or more distinct GoI Formats (at least one article for each four GoIs.)</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc16"><span>GSA</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/gsa.png" width="160px" alt="gsa.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc17"><span>Guest Star Appearance</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Write an article featuring an SCP, GoI, character or other major elements originating from a foreign branch (Bonus points if it's an obscure one!)</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc18"><span>TLT</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/tlt.png" width="160px" alt="tlt.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc19"><span>Tall Tales</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Have 10 tales published on the wiki. Parts of a bigger story count, as long as they're separate pages.</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc20"><span>TBE</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/tbe.png" width="160px" alt="tbe.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc21"><span>Team Building Exercise</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Write an article featuring two (or more) characters or GoIs who would never work together/has seldom even met deciding to cooperate for once. Bonus points if it doesn't involve the Foundation in any way.</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc22"><span>CHL</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/chl.png" width="160px" alt="chl.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc23"><span>The Challenger</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Complete at least three challenges on the <a href="/writing-challenge-list">Writing Challenges List</a>.</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc24"><span>STR</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/str.png" width="160px" alt="str.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc25"><span>Making Strides</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Have 50 pages published on the wiki.<br />
(Fragment pages still don't count, ha.)</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc26"><span>AWB</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/awb.png" width="160px" alt="awb.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc27"><span>Are We the Baddies?</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Write an article where the Foundation is explicitly an antagonistic force.</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc28"><span>CTS</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/cts.png" width="160px" alt="cts.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc29"><span>The Centurion</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Have 100 pages published on the wiki. Whoa!<br />
(You're pretty awesome, you know that?)</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc30"><span>PBS</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/pbs.png" width="160px" alt="pbs.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc31"><span>Playing for both Sites</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Be an author of both the SCP Wiki and the <a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/">Wanderer's Library</a>.</p>
</div>
<div class="caser">
<div class="codecon">
<h5 id="toc32"><span>SPA</span></h5>
</div>
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/spa.png" width="160px" alt="spa.png" class="image" />
<h1 id="toc33"><span>Student Participation Award</span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Attend two site-hosted Workshops or Seminars. Bonus points if you publish an article utilizing your newly acquired knowledge!</p>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<p>To have the badges on your page, put the following in:</p>
<div class="darkbox" style="font-family: monospace;">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[=]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;component:sybadge&#32;code=aaa]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;component:sybadge&#32;code=bbb]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/=]]</span></p>
</div>
<br />
In place of <em>aaa</em> and <em>bbb</em>, use the three-letter key at the top left of the card corresponding to your chosen badge (all lowercase).
<div style="text-align: center;">

<span class="tooltip"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/dark-achievement-badges"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/sek.png" style="background-color: var(--bgBadgeColor); padding: .66rem .7rem .4rem .5rem; border-radius: .6rem 2.5rem .6rem .6rem; margin: .3rem; border: solid 4px var(--borderColor);" width="64px" alt="sek.png" class="image" /></a><span class="tooltiptext"><span class="sek"> </span></span></span>

<span class="tooltip"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/dark-achievement-badges"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/scl.png" style="background-color: var(--bgBadgeColor); padding: .66rem .7rem .4rem .5rem; border-radius: .6rem 2.5rem .6rem .6rem; margin: .3rem; border: solid 4px var(--borderColor);" width="64px" alt="scl.png" class="image" /></a><span class="tooltiptext"><span class="scl"> </span></span></span></div>
<p>To change the color of the badge border and background, put the following:</p>
<div class="darkbox" style="font-family: monospace;">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[module&#32;CSS]]</span><br />
:root {<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;--borderColor:&#32;(COLOR&#32;HERE)&#32;!important;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;--bgBadgeColor:&#32;(COLOR&#32;HERE)&#32;!important;</span><br />
}<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/module]]</span></p>
</div>
<p>By default, the colors are #CEA0FF and #21252E, respectively.</p>
<hr />
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
